<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SnapWeb</title>
<style>
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
body {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5f00ff, #ff0080, #ff7a00);
  min-height: 100vh;
  color: white;
}
header {
  padding: 20px;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: bold;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
}
.container {
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 20px;
}
.card {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}
.user {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.mood {
  color: #ffd6f2;
  margin: 8px 0;
}
.text {
  font-size: 18px;
  margin: 12px 0;
}
.reactions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
button {
  border: none;
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  cursor: pointer;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  color: white;
}
button:hover {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
}
.nav {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  padding: 12px;
}
.nav div {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.spacer { height: 90px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>✨ SnapWeb 💜</header>

<div class="container">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="user">Duda Maia</div>
    <div class="mood">😄 Feliz</div>
    <div class="text">Hoje foi um dia incrível! Compartilhando minha vibe com o mundo ✨</div>
    <div class="reactions">
      <button>🔥 Vibrei</button>
      <button>💫 Me identifiquei</button>
      <button>🌱 Me ajudou</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="user">Pedro</div>
    <div class="mood">❤️ Apaixonado</div>
    <div class="text">A saudade bateu forte hoje.</div>
    <div class="reactions">
      <button>🖤 Forte isso</button>
      <button>💫 Me identifiquei</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="user">Ana</div>
    <div class="mood">🔥 Motivada</div>
    <div class="text">Nunca desista dos seus sonhos!</div>
    <div class="reactions">
      <button>🔥 Vibrei</button>
      <button>🌱 Me ajudou</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="spacer"></div>
</div>

<div class="nav">
  <div>🏠<br>Início</div>
  <div>🔍<br>Explorar</div>
  <div>➕<br>Criar</div>
  <div>👤<br>Perfil</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
